    <file>tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Services/Ai/Sessions/SessionRestoreServiceTests.cs</file>
    <file>projects/sdap-bff.api-test-suite-repair/ledgers/real-bug-ledger.md</file>
  </relevant-files>

  <steps>
    <step order="1">Load r1 ledger entry RB-T012-01 (lines ~54-118 of `real-bug-ledger.md`) for the documented bug + recommended fix. Confirm test names + line numbers cited.</step>
    <step order="2">Read `src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Sessions/SessionRestoreService.cs` focusing on `NormaliseETag` (~line 435) and `ExtractODataETag` (~lines 405-429). Confirm `Trim('"')` and `IndexOf('"')` patterns present.</step>
    <step order="3">Implement the `NormaliseETag` repair: strip exactly one matched leading+trailing `"` pair when both are present; leave value unchanged otherwise. Preserve method signature `internal static string NormaliseETag(string etag)`.</step>
    <step order="4">Implement the `ExtractODataETag` repair: replace the manual substring scan with `JsonDocument.Parse(jsonBody).RootElement.GetProperty("@odata.etag").GetString()` (or equivalent escape-aware parsing). Preserve method signature and null/missing return semantics.</step>
    <step order="5">Build the BFF: `dotnet build src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/`. Must succeed with zero new warnings.</step>
    <step order="6">Edit `tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Services/Ai/Sessions/SessionRestoreServiceTests.cs`: remove `Skip = "..."` on `NormaliseETag_StripsOuterQuotes` and `ExtractODataETag_FindsETagInJsonBody`; remove per-test `[Trait("status","real-bug-pending-fix")]` overrides (class-level `[Trait("status","repaired")]` applies).</step>
    <step order="7">Run targeted tests: `dotnet test tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/ --filter "FullyQualifiedName~SessionRestoreServiceTests"`. All must pass (2 re-enabled + existing).</step>
    <step order="8">Update `projects/sdap-bff.api-test-suite-repair/ledgers/real-bug-ledger.md` RB-T012-01 row: status → `repaired`, add fix-commit SHA placeholder + today's date.</step>
    <step order="9">Commit: `fix(bff-api): repair SessionRestoreService ETag quote handling (RB-T012-01; repaired)` — message cites ledger entry ID + resolution mode per NFR-04.</step>
    <step order="10">Update `projects/sdap.bff.api-test-suite-repair-r2/current-task.md` with completion + cited TRX/test counts + commit SHA.</step>
  </steps>

